Hi and Welcome to BoB 2.

If this is the first time you have played one of these maps, then you are in for hours of fun, excitement, and fustration XD.

The map contains 20 levels of varying difficutiles to test your skills, memory and reactions.

Please remember to set sv_airaccelerate to 100.
For best results, a 66 tick server is preferred

Many thanks to Spliff for hosting the map during the beta stages and all those who helped during the testing period. 
Your help and input is appreciated.

Also thanks to Fud and Lachy Bear for their designs and ideaâ€™s for a couple of levels.
